  "body": "The top and bottom margin of the Debugger config stuff needs an update.\r\nThe new Debugger Config currently looks like this:\r\n<img width=\"421\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6050001/99161420-24ecb100-26c0-11eb-9fe3-ff83e7010626.png\">\r\n\r\nIt used to look like this:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6050001/99161274-af341580-26be-11eb-8e15-5dc5369728f0.png)\r\n\r\nSo now the hash of the txn is not the at the top of the screen - and the first thing people see is the Debugger Configuration stuff.  I'm not sure this should be at the top.  But let's leave it there for now.  But It seems not important enough to take up so much vertical height ( 2 lines for a single checkbox).\r\n\r\nHere's a version with the spacing improved:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6050001/99161322-29649a00-26bf-11eb-9fd1-086bd934559d.png)\r\n\r\nHere's a version with the config checkbox in a collapsed card:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6050001/99161340-6597fa80-26bf-11eb-91dd-360d43bd8ae2.png)\r\n\r\nThis puts everything on a single line and makes it fit in with the rest of the page.  Although maybe we should consider putting it lower down on on the module.\r\n\r\nWe need to update docs as well\r\n(Liana)",
